The '''Kruk battle-wagon''' was a class of [[Starship/Legends|starship]] from the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. Two were used by the [[Frezh]]lix in their [[Blockade of Sif'kric|attempted blockade]] of [[Sif'kric]] in [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]].

